node.text:
What’s going on family ☺️ Shoutout to @mavglass for sponsoring tonight’s guided meditation 🧘🏾‍♂️

Let’s breathe in deeply....and release 💨💨 any tension or stress we feel. 💆🏾‍♂️ Allowing our bodies to heal from a long week ☺️

Mindfulness techniques can vary, but in general, mindfulness meditation involves a breathing practice and awareness of body and mind. Practicing mindfulness meditation doesn't require props or preparation (no need for candles, essential oils, or mantras, unless you enjoy them). To get started, all you need is a comfortable place to sit, 3 to 5 minutes of free time, and a judgment-free mindset.

If you have any questions, feel free to DM or visit @corefrequency ☺️

node.text:
Can you feel the love tonight 💚💚💚💚 Thanks again to @mavglass 💨 for sponsoring tonight’s guided meditation 🧘🏾‍♂️ if you have any question please feel free to contact me @corefrequency and follow for your daily positivity 😂💚💚

‼️Friendly Reminder‼️ 
Whenever you’re feeling overwhelmed, your body starts to tense up, your thoughts are unclear, etc...take 2-5 minutes to stop and breathe. 

Just for today, I will not be angry
Just for today, I will not worry
Just for today, I will work honestly
Just for today, I will be grateful
Just for today, I will be kind to people and every living being
